WEBVTT

00:01.567 --> 00:04.085
Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:04.120 --> 00:05.953
This particular kind of granite

00:05.954 --> 00:07.188
comes from Barre, Vermont.

00:07.189 --> 00:08.623
Get out-
Barre? Yeah.

00:08.624 --> 00:09.924
Yeah, you can take a tour

00:09.925 --> 00:11.192
of their whole
operation up there.

00:11.193 --> 00:13.161
Yeah?
Yeah, ask for a guy named Asa.

00:13.162 --> 00:15.062
Yeah?
Yeah, you can tell him I sent you.

00:15.063 --> 00:16.297
He'll, uh...
he'll do you right.

00:16.297 --> 00:17.532
He'll set me up?
Oh, sure.

00:17.533 --> 00:18.899
You see, it's got the, uh...

00:21.003 --> 00:22.403
(both chuckling)

00:22.404 --> 00:23.455
Excuse me, sir?

00:23.456 --> 00:25.657
Hey, hey, yo.
Sir.

00:25.691 --> 00:27.959
This man obviously
mistook the uniform

00:27.960 --> 00:29.627
of the United States
Postal Service

00:29.628 --> 00:31.396
for one of the common
valet there, Norm.

00:31.397 --> 00:32.729
Now that you mention it, Cliff,

00:32.731 --> 00:34.466
you know...
Mistake or not, though, the man

00:34.467 --> 00:36.168
has entrusted a
valuable possession

00:36.169 --> 00:38.103
to one who proudly
wears this uniform.

00:38.104 --> 00:40.238
As long as that man is
in that restaurant,

00:40.239 --> 00:42.274
I-I cannot shirk
the responsibility

00:42.308 --> 00:44.242
he has laid upon
these shoulders.

00:44.243 --> 00:45.910
What are you gonna do,
just hang here

00:45.911 --> 00:47.841
for a couple hours
while the guy eats?

00:48.497 --> 00:50.615
Norm, my friend,
this is a Jaguar.

00:50.649 --> 00:52.783
Jaguar plus postman equals...

00:52.818 --> 00:53.985
adventure.

00:54.019 --> 00:55.737
Let's do it.
(laughing)

